Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
display_temperature_result(25.10)            display_temperature_result(25.10)

Name
       display_temperature_result  -  Displays  the tile-based temperature map
       file generated by Sigrity Celsius

Syntax
        display_temperature_result

       [-help]

       -layer <string>

       -reset

       Displays the tile-based temperature map file generated by Sigrity  Cel-
       sius.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs the command usage and a brief description about the com-
              mand parameters.

       -layer <string>
              Displays the temperature map for the specified layer.

              Example:

              display_temperature_result -layer <Metal6>

       -reset Resets the temperature map display.

